[INFO] Recompiling the module because of changed source code.
[INFO] Compiling 19 source files with javac [debug target 21] to target/classes
[INFO] ------------------------------------------------------------------------
[INFO] BUILD SUCCESS
```

Feel free to expand on [application.conf](file:///home/rovshan/videos/conquerer-2/src/main/resources/application.conf) by connecting your active live Postgres database or implement further actors (e.g., `EconomyActor` or `CombatActor`) using the identical No-Ask design pattern.
